OL,5, A man living near a zebra crossing     
OL,6, which went viral on social media after 
OL,7, a spate of crashes has appealed for    
OL,8, help, saying he fears someone will "die
OL,9, on my doorstep".                       
OL,11,FResidents near the crossing on Horton  
OL,12,FGrange Road in west Bradford say they  
OL,13,Fwitness near misses "every day".       
OL,15,FTahir Zeb spent #1,800 on CCTV cameras 
OL,16,Fto film accidents after he felt        
OL,17,FBradford Council wasn't going to act.  
OL,19,FThe local authority said it would be   
OL,20,Fcarrying out an "immediate inspection".
